{"tid":1478312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重要提醒：點解舉美國旗同唱美國國歌work，而其他民主國家未必work？","createTime":"2019-08-16T12:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T03:28:09.000Z","uid":35776,"like":137,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"7fefc4b8ca54f911013a4b3f2f1e4bc6e9e0a012","tid":1478312,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:52:10.000Z","msg":"睇片，美國人既觀點：we need to do more <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lho8ApIrj8Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Flho8ApIrj8Y&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0TbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=de56e896\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lho8ApIrj8Y</a><br />\n<br />\n對唔少美國人而言，呢一步係喚醒左墮落緊嘅美國精神，美國立國既初心。<br />\n舉美國旗唔止係向美國政府向侵侵求助，而係向美國國民直接求助高舉美國所代表嘅自由民主價值，直接喚起為數不少美國愛國者既道德責任<br />\n<br />\n而其他民主國家呢？或者有同樣唔少嘅盟友，但總不及美國國民有強烈嘅榮譽感同維護自由民主嘅責任感。<br />\n<br />\n所以唱美國國歌呢招係針對美國國情先最有效嘅招數，"},{"pid":"9a1941f14e777b6e03ac52f4040fd31015bf1cc0","tid":1478312,"uid":31151,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:53:51.000Z","msg":"呢一著令到侵侵D選民(愛國者/大美國主義)都撐香港 迫到侵侵要出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36e54024724634c289d83f8ee67ceee2c3efe11","tid":1478312,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:54:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d30cdf110899ae0c91dc4f835cc2ad7e6c83ee22","tid":1478312,"uid":270687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9a1941f14e777b6e03ac52f4040fd31015bf1cc0","tid":1478312,"uid":31151,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:53:51.000Z","msg":"呢一著令到侵侵D選民(愛國者/大美國主義)都撐香港 迫到侵侵要出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"The Trump-Fox &amp; Friends Feedback Loop<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/v1d7UvKWh6M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fv1d7UvKWh6M&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0TbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=2dd87f05\" 